{"tid":2066890,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"得罪講句，只要敖卓軒一日仲可以留係眾志，我地都可以無限期休息","createTime":"2020-06-16T15:05:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-17T00:16:54.000Z","uid":62151,"like":34,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"d68631125bc4dcc04c02790f01781df071bc7c6c","tid":2066890,"uid":62151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T15:05:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><br />\n香港人<br />\n死嘅死<br />\n殘廢嘅殘廢<br />\n失蹤嘅失蹤<br />\n坐監嘅坐監<br />\n<br />\n有人願意付出所有<br />\n金錢，學業，家庭，身體，甚至性命<br />\n將自己本來輝煌嘅人生，未來全部無私貢獻<br />\n<br />\n另一邊廂<br />\n可以有條二打六出黎話自己做嘅野<br />\n比起我地全部人一世人做嘅野加埋多千萬倍<br />\n<br />\n知唔知比人斬斷腳果位手足我後悔到今日<br />\n到依家我都可以見到啲血同肉<br />\n<br />\n我唔理你地點諗<br />\n但係用由香港人授予嘅名譽<br />\n侮辱每一位為香港付出所有嘅兄弟姊妹<br />\n我唔相信有人可以忍受到<br />\n<br />\n既然咁好抽，無問題，依家交曬比你<br />\n眾志你想點保隻叛徒隨便你<br />\n我就當放下大假<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"da61a6d294881f7a22758849f9ee0a524d8dd708","tid":2066890,"uid":55598,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T15:06:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"550118e26fde837df4ab98ae5093cec82a30a406","tid":2066890,"uid":55598,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T15:15:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6288368298e6f573e83490f94a34f5c8b827065b","tid":2066890,"uid":94982,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T15:18:36.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d255197944210c39a7d03ff536e96eae9b1c42e","tid":2066890,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T15:23:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>敖智障一日不除<br />\n我都唔會支持香港眾志既美國戰線</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aHxzJoV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaHxzJoV.jpg&h=04224661&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n打緊美國線既<br />\n仲有<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">攬炒巴、大專學界</span></strong></span><